do óleo.

548
01:17:51,338 --> 01:17:52,638
<i>Continuem vindo.</i>

549
01:17:53,401 --> 01:17:54,887
<i>Há muito espaço.</i>

550
01:17:59,874 --> 01:18:01,657
Embaixo do convés.

551
01:18:27,234 --> 01:18:28,534
RESERVA
PRINCIPAL

552
01:18:37,557 --> 01:18:39,256
Abandonar navio!

553
01:18:39,690 --> 01:18:41,137
Abandonar navio!

554
